 simple, the I''m not the I''m not sure how what what is the English word, the the the the the big gun. Right? The the I I right?\n\nThe the simple artillery is because pick second. No. No. I''m saying about this this, you know, artillery.", "paragraphs": [{"sentences": [{"text": "War.", "start": 0.08, "end": 0.48}, {"text": "Right?", "start": 0.48, "end": 0.98}, {"text": "Regular hot war.", "start": 1.1999999, "end": 3.04}, {"text": "Right?", "start": 3.04, "end": 3.54}, {"text": "Even in Poland, we had this big problem because because of pandemia, and this was, this was under regulations of, limited freedom And, at at the the the the the the the at that time, the supposed to be presidential election.", "start": 4.16, "end": 24.169998}], "num_words": 47, "start": 0.08, "end": 24.169998}, {"sentences": [{"text": "And there was a big problem, big, big problem, you know, how to do it, in democratic way.", "start": 26.054998, "end": 32.635}, {"text": "And, it it was, by law forbidden to do it during the any freedom, you know, any under regulation of freedom, limitations.", "start": 33.09, "end": 52.1}, {"text": "Right?", "start": 52.64, "end": 53.14}, {"text": "So now by the way, now there is a a big big political affair because because, the government at that time decided that there will be, like, elections through the, correspondence, through the mails mail.", "start": 53.84, "end": 75.54}, {"text": "Right?", "start": 75.76, "end": 76.24}], "num_words": 77, "start": 26.054998, "end": 76.24}, {"sentences": [{"text": "And, but but it is forbidden important that that this this cannot be done, especially in the way they they propose that they the post offices will be the election offices.", "start": 76.24, "end": 90.159996}, {"text": "So so it was forbidden now.", "start": 94.619995, "end": 96.299995}, {"text": "This is a fear, of bigger political affair.", "start": 96.299995, "end": 99.575}, {"text": "But but, but, yes, I mean, the the elections was moved for few months